For the noodle salad, put the vegetable oil, soy sauce and honey in a large bowl and mix well.Add the cucumber, pepper and cooked noodles, season with salt and pepper and mix well.For the chilli nuts, heat the vegetable oil in a frying pan over a medium heat and fry the peanuts for 3-4 minutes. Drain off the oil and fry for a further 2-3 minutes, then add the salt and chilli and stir well to coat the nuts.Put the noodle salad in a bowl, sprinkle over the nuts and serve.